data.title: Mmmmmm!
data.text: This restaurant is super clean, the food is delicious and not salty like so many places!  The salsa bar is amazing - I recommend the guacamole dip!  Everything is fresh and very tasty.

data.title: Soso
data.text: Today is cinco de mayo so wanted something traditional for lunch. Had not tried LaFavorita in elk grove yet. Hubby and I were out shopping and when we drove past LaFavorita, we made a quick u turn and here is where we had lunch. I had the nachos with carnitas. Just so so. Carnitas didn't stack up to other caritas that I like. Guacamole was out of a bag, ick. Not good flavor. Hubby had 2 carnitas enchiladas, rice and beans. Sauce on enchiladas was really red. And beans and rice just eh. Just not much favor compared to other Mexican restaurants we really love. Probably won't be rushing back.

data.title: Not bad but not too good either
data.text: We went here a couple of weeks ago and were expecting this place to be banging since a lot of La Favoritas in Sac are pretty good. While by no means was this place bad, the food was average and the service was average too.  I think the food tasted a bit bland compared to other La Favoritas and didn't have enough flavor, however it was clean and the food was made promptly.

data.title: One of the best Taquerias in all of the Sacto area
data.text: You can't go wrong here, great carnitas, asada, pastor, and seafood.  Generous salsa bar.  Good Mexican beers on tap like Negra Modelo and Dos Equis Amber.

data.title: Fantastic
data.text: The most authentic Mexican place in town.  Great food!  Excellent el pastor, carnitas, tostadas and tortas.

data.title: Awesome new location.  All the best items too...
data.text: The owners brought this Sacramento Mexican tradition to old Elk Grove. Thank you!  I had a stop for lunch that was recommended as great food and this place sure lived up to that! I had the Taco Salad (trying to go light) and it was very good. The burritos, tacos and plate items looked awesome as well.  People were all busy eating - hum wonder why.  The parking is in the back and very tight, but it has a great outdoor seating and the food comes really fast to your table. I loved the iPad at the register to pay.  Staff was very kind and helpful.  So please tip them well.  They work very hard to make you happy. "I'll be back..."
